# Phase 1 — Admin Web (MVP) in sequence

## 1) Web Auth (proper)

* Create `/login` page (not inside `/page.tsx`)
* Store token in `localStorage`
* Add **route guard** (if no token → redirect to login)
* Create `/logout` action
* Add a simple **Topbar** showing logged-in user

**APIs:** `POST /auth/login`

---

## 2) Web Layout + Navigation

* Sidebar routes:

  * Dashboard
  * Plants
  * Users
  * Forms
  * Submissions
  * (Health optional)
* Create a shared layout component (so all pages look consistent)

---

## 3) Forms module (Admin) — core feature

### 3.1 Forms List ✅ (you started)

* list templates + filters (q, status, paging)
  **API:** `GET /forms`

### 3.2 Form Detail (read-only view)

* open template details (fields list, plant scope)
  **API:** `GET /forms/{id}`

### 3.3 Create New Form (Drag & Drop Builder)

* add fields
* reorder fields (dnd-kit)
* edit field config (dropdown options)
* save as DRAFT
  **API:** `POST /forms`

### 3.4 Edit Draft Form

* update title/plantIds/fields
  **API:** `PATCH /forms/{id}`

### 3.5 Publish / Clone / Archive

* publish DRAFT
* clone published → new DRAFT version
* archive published
  **APIs:**
* `POST /forms/{id}/publish`
* `POST /forms/{id}/clone`
* `POST /forms/{id}/archive`

### 3.6 Import Form (Excel→JSON)

* upload excel in UI → convert → preview → send JSON
  **API:** `POST /forms/import`

---

## 4) Plants module (Admin)

* list plants
* create plant
  **APIs:** `GET /plants`, `POST /plants`

---

## 5) Users module (Admin)

* users list + filters
* create manager (assign plantIds)
* edit user (role, plantIds, active)
* enable/disable
  **APIs:**
* `GET /users`
* `POST /users/managers`
* `PATCH /users/{id}`
* `PATCH /users/{id}/enable`
* `PATCH /users/{id}/disable`

---

## 6) Submissions module (Admin review)

* list submissions (filters: plantId/status/search/pagination)
* submission detail (with template+field meta)
* approve / reject with reason
* photo view
  **APIs:**
* `GET /mobile/forms/submissions`
* `GET /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}`
* `POST /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}/approve`
* `POST /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}/reject`
* `GET /files/signed-url`

---

