# Phase 2 — Mobile App (MVP) in sequence

## 1) Mobile Auth

* login screen
* store token in secure storage (Expo SecureStore)
* role-based navigation (USER vs MANAGER)
  **API:** `POST /auth/login`

---

## 2) Plant selection (shared)

* show plants user has access to
* store selected plantId locally
  **API:** `GET /plants` (or decode from token, but better to show names)

---

## 3) USER flow (forms filling)

### 3.1 Published Forms List

* show templates for selected plant
  **API:** `GET /mobile/forms?plantId=...`

### 3.2 Form Fill Screen (dynamic renderer)

* render TEXT/NUMBER/CHECKBOX/DROPDOWN/DATE/PHOTO
* local validation
* photo upload inside form
  **API:** `POST /files/upload?folder=photos`

### 3.3 Submit

**API:** `POST /mobile/forms/submissions`

### 3.4 My Submissions

* list mine + filters by status
  **API:** `GET /mobile/forms/submissions/mine`

### 3.5 Submission Detail + photo view

**APIs:**

* `GET /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}`
* `GET /files/signed-url`

---

## 4) MANAGER flow (review)

### 4.1 Review queue

* list submissions (default SUBMITTED)
* filter by plant/status/search
  **API:** `GET /mobile/forms/submissions`

### 4.2 Review detail

**API:** `GET /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}`

### 4.3 Approve/Reject

**APIs:**

* `POST /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}/approve`
* `POST /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}/reject`

---

## 5) Mobile polish

* TanStack Query
* offline-friendly UX later (optional)
* photo viewer UX (zoom)

---

